pipelineIntegration.promptInjectionTemplate:
ACTIVE NUTRITION CONTRACT:
Authority: {{contractType}} — {{source}}
User goal: {{patientProfile.goal}}
Conditions: {{constraints.conditions}}

FBDG BASELINE RULES (always active):
{{DEFAULT.llmInstructions joined by newline}}

{{IF conditions match FBDG conditionTables}}CONDITION-SPECIFIC FBDG RULES ({{conditionTable key}}):
USE: {{conditionTable.use}}
REDUCE: {{conditionTable.reduceIntake}}
AVOID: {{conditionTable.avoid}}
COOKING NOTES: {{conditionTable.cookingNotes}}
{{END IF}}

{{IF userContract exists}}USER NUTRITIONIST REPORT RULES (override FBDG where they conflict):
{{userContract.llmInstructions joined by newline}}
Additional hard exclusions: {{userContract.constraints.contraindications}}
Dinner rules: {{userContract.constraints.dinnerRules}}
Portion rules: {{userContract.constraints.portionRules}}
{{END IF}}
